headline: Why Welltower (WELL) Is Up 12.1% After Raising 2026 Guidance And Highlighting FFO Momentum
summary: In early February 2026, Welltower Inc. reported past fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 results showing strong revenue growth to US$3.18 billion for the quarter and US$10.84 billion for the year, but slightly lower net income and earnings per share alongside new 2026 net income guidance of US$2.24–US$2.36 billion and a continued quarterly dividend of US$0.74 per share.
